data.description: Well kept one owner home with lots of updates. New vinyl siding in 2022, roof replaced in 2006, all windows replaced including new kitchen windows in 2022. All stainless steel appliances are newer including new Bosch dishwasher in 2021 and newer double oven. New carpet throughout house in 2022.Laminate flooring in dining room and living room. New double sink vanity and fixtures, and lighting in main bath which includes a corner jetted tub and separate shower and tons of storage space. Vaulted ceiling in primary bedroom with walk-in closet. Lower level features gas fireplace in family room and separate wet bar room. Home has new concrete driveway, high efficient furnace and A/C new in 2013. Water heater new in 2006. Roof replaced in 2006 with 30-year timberline shingles. Beautiful large lawn with in-ground irrigation system.
